ISLAMABAD, Feb 23 (APP): Federal Minister for Maritime Affairs Ali Haider Zaidi on Tuesday said that the reign of terror in Sindh by PPP reminded me how Hitler’s “Brownshirt” goons & “Gestapo Police beat up political opponents in Nazi Germany”.
In a tweet, he said that Bilawal Bhutto Zardari, Chairman Pakistan People’s Party (PPP) should stop crying and look at what his own government is doing? but looks like he is an aider & abettor.
